quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,44,ya tum yeh khayaal karte ho ke un mein aksar suntay ya samajte hain ( nahi ) yeh to chopaiyon ki terhan hain balkay un se bhi ziyada gumraah hain
  25,45,balkay tum ne apne perwar-digaar ( ki qudrat ) ko nahi dekha ke woh saaye ko kis terhan daraaz kar ( ke phela ) deta hai. aur agar woh chahta to is ko ( be harkat )tehra rakhta phir Sooraj ko is ka rehnuma bana deta hai
  25,46,phir is ko hum aahista aahista apni taraf samaitt letay hain
  25,47,aur wohi to hai jis ne raat ko tumahray liye parda aur neend ko aaraam banaya aur din ko aُth kharray honay ka waqt thehraya
  25,48,aur wohi to hai jo apni rehmat kemeinhہ ke agay hawaon ko khush khaberi bana kar bhejta hai. aur hum aasman se pak ( aur nthra howa ) pani barastee hain
  25,49,taakay is se shehar murda ( yani zameen aftada ) ko zindah kar dein aur phir usay bohat se chopaiyon aur admion ko jo hum ne peda kiye hain pilate hain
  25,50,aur hum ne is ( quran ki ayaton ) ko terhan terhan se logon mein bayankiya taakay nasiyaat pakren magar bohat se logon ne inkaar ke siwa qubool nahkiya
  25,51,aur agar hum chahtay to har bastii mein darane wala bhaij dete
  25,52,to tum kafiroon ka kaha nah manu aur un se is quran ke hukum ke mutabiq barray shdomd se lrho
  25,53,aur wohi to hai jis ne do daryaaon ko mila diya aik ka pani sheree hai pyaas bujhanay wala aur dosray ka khaari chhaati jalanay wala. aur dono ke darmain aik aarr aur mazboot oot bana di
  25,54,aur wohi to hai jis ne pani se aadmi pedakiya. phir is ko sahib nasb aur sahib qaraabat دامادی banaya. aur tumhara perwar-digaar ( har terhan ki ) qudrat rakhta hai
  25,55,aur yeh log khuda ko chore kar aisi cheez ki parastish kar te hain jo nah un ko faida pouncha sakay aur nah zarrar. aur kafir apne perwar-digaar ki mukhalfat mein bara zor maarta hai
